613
00:55:22,890 --> 00:55:26,712
For the female of the species is
more deadly than the male...”

614
00:55:47,561 --> 00:55:50,791
If I can’t hear you then
I can’t see you.

615
00:55:50,826 --> 00:55:53,696
And if I can’t see you
then you are not here.

616
00:55:53,731 --> 00:55:57,495
And if you are not here,
I am not going mad.

617
00:55:57,530 --> 00:55:59,008
I will not go mad.

618
00:55:59,043 --> 00:56:02,872
I will not...
I will not go mad.

619
00:56:05,206 --> 00:56:09,492
Baroness Thatcher made an apparently
routine visit to her doctor today.

620
00:56:09,527 --> 00:56:11,621
Although rarely seen in public,

621
00:56:11,656 --> 00:56:14,972
the longest serving Prime Minister
of the twentieth century,

622
00:56:15,007 --> 00:56:17,270
remains a controversial figure.

623
00:56:17,639 --> 00:56:21,072
Almost lovingly dubbed by the
Soviets The Iron Lady,

